snippet: Australia have included spinners Stephen O'Keefe and Ashton Agar in their squad for the third and final test against Pakistan in Sydney after taking an unassailable 2-0 series lead in Melbourne with an innings and 18-run victory on Friday....
lead_paragraph: Australia have included spinners Stephen O'Keefe and Ashton Agar in their squad for the third and final test against Pakistan in Sydney after taking an unassailable 2-0 series lead in Melbourne with an innings and 18-run victory on Friday.

headline.main: Australia Look to Twin-Spin Attack in Sydney
headline.print_headline: Australia Look to Twin-Spin Attack in Sydney
